OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry and
OL,6,Fsunny evening. Lengthy clear spells
OL,7,Fovernight will allow areas of fog to
OL,8,Fdevelop, with frost likely especially
OL,9,Fin prone rural spots. Cloud may linger
OL,10,Fnear coastal parts.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FA cold start once again, but
OL,13,Fwith early frost and fog soon clearing
OL,14,Fto leave another dry and sunny day.
OL,15,FWarmer than Thursday, but remaining
OL,16,Fcooler near coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
